snippet.title: LISA: The Hopeful - Definitive Update (1.14)
snippet.description:
A fangame set in the world of LISA. Thanks for playing. Game is at patch 1.14 with a lot of fixes and changes.

Track is Garbage by Taitoki - https://taitoki.bandcamp.com/album/sounds-of-lisa
